author: Disney
description:
Michelle Khare is here for an episode of Movie Surfers on “Avatar: Fire and Ash.” Dive back into the far-off planet of Pandora for an exclusive, behind-the-scenes look at the third installment of James Cameron’s phenomenally successful “Avatar” franchise. Watch the full Movie Surfers episode now on YouTube. Experience “Avatar: Fire and Ash” only in theatres on December 19th, 2025.
